8 bit addition:-

MVI C,00
LDA 100
MOV B,A
LDA 101
ADD B
JNC skip
INR C ; c=C+1
skip: STA 102
MOV A,C
STA 103
HLT

8 bit subtraction:-

MVI C,00
LDA 100
MOV B,A
LDA 101
SUB B
JNC skip
INR C 
skip: STA 102
MOV A,C
STA 103
HLT

8bit multiplication:-

LXI H,100
MOV B,M 
MVI A,00 
MOV C,A 
INX H 
CONT: ADD M 
JNC SKIP 
INR C
SKIP: DCR B
JNZ CONT 
STA 102
MOV A,C
STA 103
HLT

8bit division:-

LXI H, 1001

MOV B,M

MVI C,00

INX H

loop: CMP B

JC skip

SUB B

INR C

JMP loop

skip: STA 102

MOV A, C

STA 103

HLT

AND GATE:-

MVI A, 06
MVI B, 04
ANA B
STA 200
 HLT

OR GATE:-

MVI A, 07
MVI B, 06
ORA B
STA 200
HLT

XOR GATE:-

MVI A, 03
MVI B, 04
XRA B
STA 200
HLT

ROTATE RIGHT ACCUMULATOR:-

6MVI A, 03
RRC; Rotate Right Accumluator
RRC
RRC
RRC
STA 200
HLT

RIGHT LEFT ACCUMULATOR:-

MVI A, 02
RLC; Right Left Accumulator
RLC
RLC
RLC
STA 200
HLT

1's and 2's compliment:-


LDA 200
CMA
STA 201
ADI 01
STA 202
HLT

Find larger Number

MVI A, 66
MVI B, 34
CMP B
JC LABEL_B
JMP LABEL A
LABEL A: STA 200
JMP END
LABEL B: MOV A, B
STA 200
END: HLT


Finding smaller number:-

MVI A, 66
MVI B, 34
CMP B
JC LABEL A
JMP LABEL_B
LABEL A: STA 200
JMP END
LABEL B: MOV A,B
STA 200
END: HLT
